      <title>凯雷重启化学公司 Nouryon 的 IPO 计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/carlyle-revives-ipo-plans-for-chemical-firm-nouryon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在全球私募股权公司准备迎接上市反弹之际，凯雷集团已重启特种化学品生产商诺力昂 (Nouryon) 的首次公开募股 (IPO) 计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/carlyle-revives-ipo-plans-for-chemical-firm-nouryon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 17:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布克莱发出零赤字信号后，萨尔瓦多债券飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/el-salvador-bonds-soar-after-bukele-signals-zero-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨尔瓦多总统纳伊布·布克尔表示，2025 年预算不会涉及发行新债，这表明他计划实施财政紧缩政策，这是启动与国际货币基金组织期待已久的计划的关键一步。随后，萨尔瓦多主权债务周一大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/el-salvador-bonds-soar-after-bukele-signals-zero-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦丹塔氧化铝厂水厂泄漏事故未影响产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/aluminum-prices-jump-after-another-alumina-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韦丹塔有限公司 (Vedanta Ltd.) 表示，周一印度一家工厂的蓄水设施发生溢流，预计其氧化铝生产不会受到任何影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/aluminum-prices-jump-after-another-alumina-disruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
